title: 10 year anniversary
body: i have received the icon but I haven't received the mystery gift as I already own kayle and the riot kayle skin

replies.body: The gifts are being sent out separately, and it's unlikely you'll get it all at once because there are so many eligible accounts.  We'll have our progress updated in our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight until this is all done!

The gifts are handed out separately, not at the same time, so it's normal to receive one without receiving the other yet. Just hang tight as the rewards are not done being distributed. The final day is the 23rd, so if you don't receive everything by then, you can submit a support ticket.
